{
  "title": "Smoky Flaky Japanese Jersey Royal Potatoes Stir-fry",
  "description": "A quick-fix, paleo-friendly dish featuring smoky and flaky Jersey Royal potatoes in a simple stir-fry with minimal added fats.",
  "cuisine": "Japanese",
